For those of you who may not know, the Special Olympic Games are aimed at athletes with intellectual disabilities.
The Special Olympic Games are separate from the Paralympic and Olympic Games.
We offer high-quality sporting programs all year round for people with intellectual disabilities, which changes lives and perceptions.
This movement has changed my life and that of so many others.
